title: Jaggery Thekua | गुड़ ठेकुआ | Khajuria | Tikari | Thokni

title: Anarsa | अनरसा
description: Anarsa is a festive Bihari sweet made with rice flour and jaggery, coated in poppy seeds and deep-fried to perfection. Each bite offers a nutty crunch and mellow sweetness. Handmade with traditional methods, Anarsa is perfect for special occasions and festive boxes.

title: Mudhi Lai | मुढ़ी लाई
description: Mudhi Lai is a beloved Bihari treat made with puffed rice (mudhi) and molten jaggery. Shaped into crunchy, sweet balls, they bring back the essence of rural Bihar. These guilt-free sweets are handmade using fresh jaggery and locally sourced rice, making them a simple yet wholesome snack.

title: Namak Para | Nimki (Atta) | नमक पारा | निमकी (आटा)
description: Namak Para, also known as Nimki in Bihar, is a crunchy, salty snack perfect with evening chai. Made using whole wheat (atta) and seasoned with carom seeds (ajwain), these golden diamond-shaped bites are deep-fried till crisp. A favorite during festivals and family gatherings.

title: Pantua | पन्तुआ
description: Pantua is Bihar’s cousin to the Gulab Jamun — deeper in color and richer in taste. Made from khoya and deep-fried to perfection, it is soaked in cardamom-infused syrup and served warm or cold. Each bite is soft, juicy, and nostalgic, crafted in small batches at Bihar Ke Swaad’s home kitchen.

title: Laung Lata | लौंग लता
description: Laung Lata is a traditional Bihari dessert filled with khoya and dry fruits, wrapped in a crispy pastry and soaked in flavored sugar syrup. Known for its signature clove (laung) in the center, this sweet delivers rich texture and festive warmth. Handmade with care, it’s an iconic delicacy from Bihar’s sweet heritage.

title: Balushahi | बालूशाही
description: Balushahi, a flaky and golden sweet from Bihar, is a celebration in every bite. Prepared with pure desi ghee and dipped in sugar syrup, it’s a festive favorite that melts in your mouth. At Bihar Ke Swaad, every Balushahi is handmade using traditional recipes and high-quality ingredients, ensuring authenticity and taste that reminds you of home.
